    "security-fencing-and-metal-cage-installation-irvine": "Security fencing and metal cage installation in Greater Glasgow. Maximum security solutions for commercial and industrial properties. Professional installation, free quotes.",
    "deck-construction-irvine": "Deck construction in Greater Glasgow. Professional deck building from scratch. Quality materials, expert craftsmanship, free quotes available.",
